ars as a scientist and engineer, as Chief Technologist, reviewing all of NASA\'s R&D in every field of endeavor for the NASA Inventions and Contributions Board and the NASA Administrator;\n\nOwns 20 invention disclosures, 5 patents, 85 scientific and technical peer-reviewed papers, 42 years in the profession, and successfully completed 15 projects on time, on budget, and meeting or exceeding specifications;\n\nListed in \"Who\'s Who in America\" for 2009 through 2014, also as \"Who\'s Who In The World\" in 2010 to 2014.\n\nSpecialties: All forms of engineering and science; management, economics, finance, political and social issues and constraints, business, venture capitalism.\n\nDesigned first all-solar home for Ryland Homes in 1974. At MITRE, led a group of 35 of the best minds in the world (including Dr. Edward Teller, among others) who performed detailed engineering, scientific, socio-economic, and political analyses of all alternative energy choices for ERDA/DOE, NSF, and MITRE in 1975-80, and designed solar power plants at Gibbs & Hill in \'80-\'83.</em>','Conselho','','inherit','open','open','','2411-revision-v1','','','2013-11-26 13:49:46','2013-11-26 13:49:46','',2411,'http://biospace.trafego.biz/dev/2411-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(2593,1,'2013-11-25 18:27:45','2013-11-25 18:27:45','<h3>Empresas</h3>\r\nParallax Inc. - <a href=\"http://www.parallax.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.parallax.com</a>\r\n\r\n<h3>Observações</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sites</h3>\r\n<p>Inovação Tecnológica - <a href=\"http://www.inovacaotecnologica.com.br/\" target=\"_blank\">www.inovacaotecnologica.com.br</a></p>\r\n<p>Laboratório de Garagem - <a href=\"http://labdegaragem.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.labdegaragem.com</a></p>\r\n','Inspiração','','publish','open','open','','inspiracao','','','2013-11-26 15:16:24','2013-11-26 15:16:24','',2617,'http://biospace.trafego.biz/dev/?page_id=2593',0,'page','',0),(2594,1,'2013-11-25 18:27:45','2013-11-25 18:27:45','','Inspiração','','inherit','o